OL,3,CVigil to take place in memory of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler
OL,6,FHundreds of people are expected to
OL,7,Fgather for a candlelight vigil in
OL,8,Fmemory of a 13-month-old toddler who
OL,9,Fwas murdered by his adoptive father.
OL,11,FThe memorial for Preston Davey will
OL,12,Ftake place at the Preston Flag Market
OL,13,Fat 8pm on 16 June - marking what would
OL,14,Fhave been the little boy's fourth
OL,15,Fbirthday.
OL,17,FMembers of the public are being asked
OL,18,Fto "bring candles, bubbles, teddies"
OL,19,Fand "remember that sweet boy."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
