OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781722095
OL,3,CVigil to take place in memory of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler
OL,6,FThe vigil follows an trial at Preston
OL,7,FCrown Court, which revealed the abuse
OL,8,FPreston suffered at the hands of Jamie
OL,9,FVarley, 37, and his partner, John
OL,10,FMcGowan-Fazakerley, 32.
OL,12,FThe court heard how Preston was
OL,13,Froutinely ill-treated, physically
OL,14,Fassaulted, and sexually abused while
OL,15,Fin their care for just under four
OL,16,Fmonths at their home in Blackpool.
OL,18,FThe jury was told the toddler had
OL,19,Fsuffered 40 traumatic injuries before
OL,20,Fhis death on 27 July 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781722095
OL,3,CVigil to take place in memory of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler
OL,6,FFollowing an eight-week trial, a jury
OL,7,Fspent around 14 hours considering
OL,8,Fverdicts before it returned to court.
OL,10,FJamie Varley was found guilty of
OL,11,Fmurder, two counts of assault by
OL,12,Fpenetration, five counts of cruelty to
OL,13,Fa child, grievous bodily harm, sexual
OL,14,Fassault of a child, and 13 counts of
OL,15,Ftaking indecent photos or videos of a
OL,16,Fchild. He was also convicted of making
OL,17,Fand distributing indecent images.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
