PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781722095
OL,3,CVigil to take place in memory of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler
OL,6,FJohn McGowan-Fazakerley was found
OL,7,Fguilty of allowing the death of a
OL,8,Fchild, two counts of child cruelty,
OL,9,Fand one count of the sexual assault of
OL,10,Fa child.
OL,12,FSpeaking after the verdicts, Karen
OL,13,FTonge of the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,14,F(CPS) condemned the actions of the
OL,15,Fpair.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781722095
OL,3,CVigil to take place in memory of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler
OL,6,FShe said: "No child should have to go
OL,7,Fthrough what Preston went through in
OL,8,Fthe last four months of his short life
OL,9,Fand I cannot begin to imagine the toll
OL,10,Fthis has taken on those that loved
OL,11,FPreston. My thoughts remain with them
OL,12,Fall."
OL,14,FFollowing the convictions, Oldham
OL,15,FCouncil confirmed it will re-launch a
OL,16,Fformal child safeguarding practice
OL,17,Freview, which had been paused while
OL,18,Fcriminal proceedings took place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
